gitCommit.subject: perf(ci): disable sharding for E2E tests - run all tests in single job
gitCommit.body:
perf(ci): disable sharding for E2E tests - run all tests in single job

- Changed shard matrix from [1,2,3,4] to [1]
- Combined with workers:1 for fully sequential execution
- Improves stability by eliminating race conditions between shards
